## ✔ What I Learned
- Dataset tells ADF exactly which file/folder to read.
- Dataset uses a Linked Service to connect to the storage.
- CSV dataset is for raw data.
- Parquet dataset is for optimized data (Silver/Gold layer).

## ✔ What I Created
1. CSV Dataset:
   - Name: DS_Healthcare_CSV
   - File System: raw
   - File Name: patients.csv
   - Linked Service: LS_ADLS_Healthcare

2. Parquet Dataset:
   - Name: DS_Healthcare_Parquet
   - File System: silver
   - Directory: blank
   - File Name: blank
   - Linked Service: LS_ADLS_Healthcare

## ✔ Why This Matters
Datasets are required to read/write data in pipelines and dataflows.

